/div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- SECONDI -->\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-[1.4rem] font-bold text-blue-500\">Secondi Piatti</h2>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shadow-md p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 image-loader\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n        <img src=\"/image_search_cse?dish=Polpo%20in%20Acqua%20Sua&amp;city=Bari\" class=\"w-[260px] min-w-[260px] h-[220px] object-cover rounded-[14px] flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Polpo in Acqua Sua\" data-image-source=\"cse\" data-loader-bound=\"1\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center w-full\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Polpo in Acqua Sua</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-[0.95rem] text-[#4b5a56]\">Polpo cotto lentamente con pomodoro e aromi, semplice ma ricco di gusto.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shadow-md p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 image-loader\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n        <img src=\"/image_search_cse?dish=Braciole%20al%20Sugo&amp;city=Bari\" class=\"w-[260px] min-w-[260px] h-[220px] object-cover rounded-[14px] flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Braciole al Sugo\" data-image-source=\"cse\" data-loader-bound=\"1\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center w-full\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Braciole al Sugo</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-[0.95rem] text-[#4b5a56]\">Involtini di carne tenerissima ripieni e cotti per ore nel sugo di pomodoro.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shadow-md p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 image-loader\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n        <img src=\"/image_search_cse?dish=Seppie%20Ripiene%20al%20Sugo&amp;city=Bari\" class=\"w-[260px] min-w-[260px] h-[220px] object-cover rounded-[14px] flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Seppie Ripiene al Sugo\" data-image-source=\"cse\" data-loader-bound=\"1\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center w-full\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Seppie Ripiene al Sugo</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-[0.95rem] text-[#4b5a56]\">Seppie farcite con un ripieno saporito e cotte in un ricco sugo di pomodoro.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ================= VINI ================= -->\n  \n\n  <!-- ================= COSA ACQUISTARE ================= -->\n  <section class=\"pb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-[1.4rem] font-bold mb-4\">Cosa Acquistare</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\">\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shadow-md p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 image-loader\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n          <img src=\"/image_search_cse?dish=Orecchiette%20Fresche&amp;city=Bari\" class=\"w-[260px] min-w-[260px] h-[220px] object-cover rounded-[14px] flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Orecchiette Fresche\" data-image-source=\"cse\" data-loader-bound=\"1\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center w-full\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Orecchiette Fresche</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-[0.95rem] text-[#4b5a56]\">Simbolo della cucina barese, spesso preparate a mano nei vicoli di Bari Vecchia.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shadow-md p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 image-loader\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n          <img src=\"/image_search_cse?dish=Focaccia%20Barese&amp;city=Bari\" class=\"w-[260px] min-w-[260px] h-[220px] object-cover rounded-[14px] flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Focaccia Barese\" data-image-source=\"cse\" data-loader-bound=\"1\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center w-full\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Focaccia Barese</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-[0.95rem] text-[#4b5a56]\">Soffice e croccante, condita con pomodorini e olive, ideale come street food.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-[18px] shado